Task: Implement Quilter API integration (kbd_engine/routers/quilter.py)
Summary of changes:
- Created QuilterRouter class delegating routing requests to Quilter's REST API.
- Implemented authentication, POST /jobs submission of DSN payload, and GET /jobs/job_id polling loop.
- Reused FreeRouting's DSN exporter and SES/S-expression parser for request serialization and response deserialization.
- Wrote tests in tests/test_quilter.py mock-testing successful submission/polling, authentication failures, rate limiting, job timeouts, and unroutable board failure states.
Why: Exposes Quilter AI autorouting service as an optional routing backend.
